# Sales Performance Images

This folder contains screenshots from the Sales Performance Analytics Tableau dashboard. These images provide a visual overview of key findings related to revenue trends, product performance, customer demographics, geographic sales distribution, and payment method preferences.

## Contents

- Full dashboard screenshot
- Revenue by Category horizontal bar chart
- Top 5 Products horizontal bar chart
- Top 5 Cities horizontal bar chart
- Revenue by Age Group bar chart
- Revenue by Month line chart
- Revenue by Payment Method treemap
